called a curl. Turati sat down to play with a German grandmaster and Luzhin came up to her and gloomily, with a guilty smile, said something long and clumsy. She realized with surprise that he was asking her to leave.

'I'm glad, I'm very glad post factum,' explained Luzhin pleadingly, 'but for the moment... for the moment it somehow disturbs me.' He followed her with his eyes as she obediently withdrew between the rows of chess tables and after nodding briskly to himself, he made his way to the